Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.70,0:00:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会说自己的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是菲布莉妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都行  知道什么告诉我什么好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂美琴?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.27,0:00:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?  会不会是御坂学姐认识的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.48,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲戚?  表妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同父异母的妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的「妹妹」已经够多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道是姐姐大人的孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都有我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:01:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是御坂美琴  你是怎样认识我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来小孩子是懂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁危险  谁安全
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.55,0:01:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指玩偶?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饮料的赠品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没中就一直让我陪著她喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是那么喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  我是呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你告诉我一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那封入率二十四分之一的粉色呱太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  别为了一个两个手指玩偶就大声嚷嚷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能擅自拿别人的东西吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.58,0:02:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全把你当安全地点了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖  那个呱太玩偶是美琴姐姐的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖还给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  是菲布莉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…在走失孩子和失踪者中没有她的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.96,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642.667,645.333)}<Antiskill>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚了也无法与警备员的负责人取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今晚她就由我来看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们瞧她已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有弟弟  已经习惯照顾小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能拜托你一晚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家太小了  一个人的话怕照顾不过来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢  初春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.99,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔舔?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你  在这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肚子饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们开工了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子他娘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开动咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是牛肉饼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把眼睛紧紧闭上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么轮到菲布莉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我浇水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  会摔倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子  你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个调皮小妮子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  初春  快来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初初
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背影略显阴霾哦  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不在乎呢  就是个赠品而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.34,0:07:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个手指玩偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.09,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不挺在乎的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会那么怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说姐姐大人喜欢那个幼女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人  你是这个意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有觉悟  为了姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宝贝…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:08:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白井  你在鬼叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过说真的  她怎么会知道我的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个孩子有点特别呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道的确很重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然舔得那么若无其事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐天  你太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:09:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚跟我说「超好吃的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果让我也舔了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是都道歉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是找不到她的资料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也向失踪以及走失人口的数据库提交了信息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过目前还没有回应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.56,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,646)}<Child Error>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  她或许是弃童
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬家的事安顿好了  就来向你们打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子真让人操心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.14,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(659,646)}<Child Error>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是弃童吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经用了不少方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可还是查不到她的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就只能等设施的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿她能去个好一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还分好坏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说有的设施条件环境很差的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能选去处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初春  没有关于设施评价排行之类的资料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那么就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经和对方确认好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好像答应接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说可以去「明日桧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在13学区的设施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经去拜访过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个暖人心脾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:02.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好接收手续最快也要5天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前就由我来好好照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我也帮忙呗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我如是转达给对方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.58,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿意暂时和我们一起生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和涙子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呀  还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初初也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有黒子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有美伟?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:40.82,banner,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs55\3c&H8D92B0&\b0\pos(1181.87,261.466)}{\c&H0938E0&}{\c&H0938E0&\3c&H7D8BB1&}#\N20\N菲\N布\N莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那在学究会之前都能在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:12:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  差不多到商讨会场警备的时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.09,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再来玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次也叫上绊理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了  菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  衿衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连对春上都那么友善!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要让她叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这里真的是学究会的会场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  好像没什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学究会与能力无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单纯是个发表学术研究成果的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉是缺乏几分华丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了痴狂的地步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的样子格外失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想像中的是什么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  就是那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有露天摊啊  还有很多活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都住在那里通宵准备啊  之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  所以才一起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那种感觉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子也不会无聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:20.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  这不是御坂同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你们怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.40,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚后光子  你怎么在这…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫泡浮万彬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:41.30,small,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  湾内她们的学姐要参加学究会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是去帮忙准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是我和泡浮的熟人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可婚后同学她还是自愿来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我出马  准备工作瞬间就能完成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.26,0:14:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  御坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是谁的妹妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚后同学  这位可爱的小妹妹叫菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚刚和她交上朋友了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  请务必也和我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫婚后光子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉  请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  请多多指教  光子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:37.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又交上了一个朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连婚后都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就去开会咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.52,0:14:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就四下转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.67,small,NTP,0,0,0,,集合地点在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我查查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会场真是够大的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了初春  洗手间在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在…那我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我回来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能乖乖地和美琴姐姐一起等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先暂时离开  你把握好机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们在这等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  这地方也太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫人员要是再多点…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  送货地点应该是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按文件上来说是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们是没有权签收的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是学究会的赞助品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责签收的学生还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是常在学究会里获奖的学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年其他的会场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常获奖学校好像几乎都还没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没  我刚才好像看到常获奖学校的学生走过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到会场了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些货物也平安送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那发现对象后再联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你饿不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要喝饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那朵花好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子还不回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真心难对付
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为我挺招小朋友喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  怎能就此气馁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  就算再被抢去也在所不惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稀有中的稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就靠这个封入率六十分之一的彩虹呱太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工还真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  可爱的小萝莉…呃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呱太碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我稍微没盯住就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  应该走不了多远的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.54,0:18:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御坂同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子…初初…黒子…美伟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已发现对象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衿衣…光子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢天谢地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涙子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是她本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来遇到了这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好没出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我没看好她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉  佐天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也应该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  菲布莉也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可让美琴姐姐担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲布莉
